channel.title: Appriciate someones help please
channel.description:
ok well when i first started playing moparscape i'd open it and it would only open the black box. A few months later(a week ago or so) i try opening it and it opens but only hybridscape will work but then i finally got servers to start working. Every once in a while i'd get frustrated because a server would work for a while, like 4 hours total and then i'd have to shut down the computer for it to work again or several times. And then one time i shut it down and turn it back on it won't work and i keep shutting it down and that and it just won't work and even today it still won't. Just a little bit ago like today i tryed hybridscape just to spawn items and stuff so that does not work. I try logging in and i spawn something and it has a connection lost and loggs me out, i try logging in again I'm already logged in or error of that sort.
I downloaded Moparscape 3.1
1 other thing, I'm not the smart when it comes to....practicly anything on the computer so try not to use such big words please
THANK YOU FOR READING
